                        Calls for a willingness to climate solutions
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[11.06.2009]</p>
                <p>The world needs an ambitious climate agreement  for us to avoid further serious climate change. Such an agreement must be based on what science tells us that is necessary to stabilize the global climate, not just what we think is politically possible.</p>
                
                
